COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 381, L.D. 613
1 SUMMARY
22 This amendment, which is the majority report of the committee, clarifies the process
33 for a qualified patient to make oral and written requests for a prescription for medication
44 to end the qualified patient's life.
